<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20921>
    dc:description "Habitus 12. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis peccans. Scale bar, 1 mn." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20921" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20948>
    dc:description "Map 12. The known distribution of Pachybrachis peccans in eastern Canada. SR - Saguenay River." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20948" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20858>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Eyes: a close eyes, Pachybrachis pectoralis b normal eyes, Pachybrachis peccans c normal eyes and yellow face, male Pachybrachis atomarius d remote eyes, Pachybrachis hepaticus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20858" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20859>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Ocular lines: a present, Pachybrachis peccans b small, Pachybrachis hepaticus c absent, Pachybrachis spumarius." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20859" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20861>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Claws: a, b front claws enlarged c, d normal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20861" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

